to\": 392}, {\"ngram\": \"the greatest athletes\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 439}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 461}, {\"ngram\": \"over 300 events\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 480}, {\"ngram\": \"32 sports\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fan favorites such as basketball, soccer, and track & field will be contested, as well as newer sports like breaking, sport climbing, and skateboarding.\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 651, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fan favorites\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 512}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 531}, {\"ngram\": \"soccer\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 550}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 558}, {\"ngram\": \"newer sports\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 601}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 615}, {\"ngram\": \"sport climbing\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The competition for medals will undoubtedly be intense, but for pure spectacle, there is no better way to get in the Olympic spirit than to watchthe Opening Ceremony.\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 802, \"end\": 818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9994045131219345, \"rank\": 0.0005957938560176038, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The competition\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 668}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 679}, {\"ngram\": \"pure spectacle\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 731}, {\"ngram\": \"no better way\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 755}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic spirit\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris has a feast for the eyes planned that is unlike any Opening Ceremony in Olympic history.\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 914, \"entities\":