1123}, {\"ngram\": \"a celebration\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic spirit\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The six-kilometer parade route will begin at the Pont d'Austerlitz and conclude with the Olympic torch being lit at the Trocadero, which is known for having some of the most spectacular views of the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1377, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The six-kilometer parade route\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"the Pont d'Austerlitz\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic torch\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"the Trocadero\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1294}, {\"ngram\": \"the most spectacular views\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1356}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1376}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The parade will pass by many of the venues that will be used in competition and will be open to all spectators, which will undoubtedly produce a record-setting attendance figure.\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1556, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The parade\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1388}, {\"ngram\": \"the venues\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"all spectators\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1488}, {\"ngram\": \"a record-setting attendance figure\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How can viewers at home enjoy the festivities, though?\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1572}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1580}, {\"ngram\": \"the festivities\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1602}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For that, we have got you covered with our handy viewing guide.\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our handy viewing guide\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1674}]}, {\"senten